These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, december, april, september
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Birthday   | may | december | september | april |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, techno, trance, disco
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of trance is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of d&b is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of trance##1
6. the fan of d&b is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | d&b | trance | techno    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, lily, poppy, begonia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Flower          | begonia | poppy | lily    | dahlia      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

