.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, orange, ebony, grey
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. the person who likes orange is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes black##1
3. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Color         | grey | black | orange | ebony |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

