.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, epic, time-travel
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, september, august, january
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| Birthday   | january | september     | may  | august  |

