.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, march, january, august
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, roller, ship
1. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person driving the ship is the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Birthday   | february | august | january | march    |
| Transport     | ship | roller  | car     | quad-bike |

