.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, pilot, project-manager, teacher
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, ambient, country, rock
1. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the pilot##3
2. the teacher is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the teacher##3
4. the teacher is on the right of the fan of rock##1
5. the coach is between the teacher and the pilot##2
6. the fan of ambient is in an odd position##4
7. the fan of ambient is between the coach and the fan of country##2
8. the coach is on the left or right of the pilot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | pilot | coach      | teacher | project-manager |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | rock | ambient    | country            |

