.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, surfing, sailing, water-polo
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Sport   | sailing | surfing | water-polo        | soccer    |

