.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, brazilian, dutch, italian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, italian-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the british##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is italian-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is italian-polo is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the brazilian is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality   | british   | italian   | brazilian      | dutch      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | italian-polo | biathlon |

