.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, car, jet-ski
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, disco, hip-hop, soul
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the car is between the fan of disco and the fan of hip-hop##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Transport          | jet-ski | helicopter  | car  | airplane |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | hip-hop | ambient | disco   |

