The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, motorbike, train
1. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
4. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
5. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | lemonade | cola | soy-milk  |
| Transport     | boat   | bike  | train  | motorbike |

