.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts, superhero, western
4 different games are played: chess, backgammon, scrabble, snooker
1. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | western | family | martial-arts |
| Game           | snooker     | chess     | scrabble   | backgammon         |

