.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, fonseca, aristoff, dannemann
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, soccer, weightlifting
1. the chaman-smoker is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the fonseca-smoker##2
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Cigar   | dannemann | fonseca         | chaman   | aristoff |
| Sport   | soccer    | skateboarding | weightlifting | ice-hockey   |

