.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, soy-milk, fanta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person drinking water##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking water is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage   | lemonade | water | soy-milk    | fanta |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

