.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, salsa, classical, jazz
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, nigerian, turkish
1. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of house##1
2. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
3. the japanese is the fan of classical##1
4. the nigerian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the japanese is between the turkish and the nigerian##2
6. the fan of salsa is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Music-Genre         | jazz   | classical | house | salsa    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | japanese  | turkish     | american |

