.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, indonesian, pakistani
4 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, go, snooker
1. the american is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing go##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the indonesian##1
5. the american is on the right of the person playing go##1
6. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indonesian | american  | pakistani |
| Game     | monopoly      | go       | backgammon | snooker     |

